Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.77,0:00:05.74,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}As we move into a new year,\Ndifficult cases get more complicated!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.74,0:00:09.34,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Today marks the second year of Conan!\NHe gets into big trouble fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.34,0:00:11.11,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.11,0:00:13.38,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.38,0:00:15.55,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
