Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.11,0:01:41.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! Are you listening to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.40,0:01:42.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.57,0:01:44.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't "eh" me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.30,0:01:48.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time since\Nyour parents transferred overseas
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.13,0:01:51.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and left you here!\NDon't you miss them?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.58,0:01:52.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.00,0:01:59.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, some parents! They don't show up once, or even call!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.75,0:02:02.59,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Oh, man... my lie's getting busted.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.22,0:02:09.56,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Though they really {\i1}are{\i0} overseas right now, so it's not really a lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.56,0:02:13.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't Dr. Agasa the one who brought him here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.31,0:02:14.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.22,0:02:19.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then shouldn't we at least ask him\Nhow to contact his parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.56,0:02:21.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.77,0:02:23.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.73,0:02:27.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not? Is there something wrong with contacting them?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.07,0:02:33.12,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Oh, man! I gotta act quick or my identity as Shin'ichi Kudo will be out of the bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:36.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's here, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.92,0:02:40.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.09,0:02:40.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.88,0:02:44.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!\NYou must've been lonely all by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.59,0:02:47.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's all right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.55,0:02:49.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now let's go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:51.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:53.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! She's not your mom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.03,0:02:59.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear me! He's just being sulky,\Nafter being left alone all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.77,0:03:06.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Fumiyo Edogawa.\NI'm Conan Edogawa's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.95,0:03:11.05,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}N-No! Conan Edogawa's an alias I invented!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.03,0:03:13.33,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}"Conan" can't possibly have parents!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:17.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate everything!\NI'll give you my thanks another day!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.33,0:03:19.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! I look forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.21,0:03:20.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.84,0:03:24.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! Send us\Na letter when you get there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:31.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss! Don't forget your thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.39,0:03:37.64,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Bye-bye, Conan{\rHonorifics - Thoughts}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.02,0:03:41.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you, lady?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.69,0:03:46.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you. I'm your mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.15,0:03:47.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope! My mom's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:49.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiko Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.45,0:03:55.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Your mother was a beautiful\NJapanese actress who enchanted men
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.75,0:04:01.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,all over the world and won all\Nthe major awards at the young age of 19.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.58,0:04:05.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But she fell in love with\Nthe young novelist Yusaku Kudo,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.27,0:04:09.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,married at 20, and then simply retired.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.01,0:04:13.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She later had a son, but left him\Nbehind to travel the world
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.35,0:04:19.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,with Yusaku Kudo, now an\Ninternationally-renowned mystery writer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:24.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right,\NShin'ichi Kudo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, their only son?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.82,0:04:31.86,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Is she with those men in black\Nwho shrunk me with their drug?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.86,0:04:33.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:40.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay still, and I'll take you to\Na nice place... A more fun place...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.04,0:04:45.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You moron, what're you doing?! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.96,0:04:47.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.71,0:04:49.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone catch that kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:03.23,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}How? How did they find out who I am?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.36,0:05:06.93,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Was it because I used\Nthe name "Shin'ichi Kudo"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.93,0:05:09.69,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}during the karaoke murder case?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.69,0:05:15.12,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}And then they heard from somewhere\Nthat I'd survived the drug...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.12,0:05:19.29,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Damn it! I told the inspector\Nnot to mention my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:26.13,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I'm so stupid! It's all my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.13,0:05:31.66,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What now, Shin'ichi Kudo?\NShould I go back and tell Ran everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.66,0:05:36.60,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}No, they'd be in danger\Nif I go back now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:41.69,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Dammit! What do I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.77,0:05:44.73,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What?! He got away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.73,0:05:50.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I was careless. But it seems\Nthe boy really {\i1}is{\i0} Shin'ichi Kudo...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:57.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. To think he really did shrink...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.28,0:06:00.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,OK. Look for him. It'll be\Na pain if he goes to the cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:02.04,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But where?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:06.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. His next destination\Nwill be probably be {\i1}there{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.15,0:06:07.24,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Agasa's House
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.46,0:06:10.71,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Guess I got no choice but to talk to Dr. Agasa,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.71,0:06:13.42,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}since he knows the situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.42,0:06:19.72,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But what's taking him so long?\NWhere is he wandering around now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.72,0:06:21.67,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.68,0:06:22.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Doc!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.69,0:06:31.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet dreams, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.28,0:06:40.74,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Where am I?! Seems to be a kitchen, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.87,0:06:44.96,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Damn it, my head's still dizzy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.54,0:06:47.92,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I'm on the first floor!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:53.63,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I see. I was carried into this\Nold house while I was unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.63,0:06:56.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You {\i1}still{\i0} haven't killed him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.22,0:06:58.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't yell at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.09,0:07:00.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Those were the orders from above...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.89,0:07:06.10,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It's that woman. And is\Nthat a man in front of her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.10,0:07:12.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The organization wants him,\Nas an example of the drug's side-effects!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.36,0:07:15.82,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Ah! So that's why she didn't kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.82,0:07:17.74,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Still, that man...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.74,0:07:19.41,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.41,0:07:25.20,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Who is that masked man?!\NOh, crap! He's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.87,0:07:29.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he awake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.17,0:07:32.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he's still drugged.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.59,0:07:37.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, is that {\i1}really{\i0} the high school\Ndetective Shin'ichi Kudo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.18,0:07:39.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I still can't believe it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.51,0:07:42.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But the day Shin'ichi Kudo\Nwent missing coincides
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.99,0:07:47.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,with the day that boy\Nappeared at that agency,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.06,0:07:51.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and all the crimes that happened\Naround him were solved easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.94,0:07:57.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing I can think of is that the organization's drug really did shrink him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.03,0:08:00.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then shall I try it, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.87,0:08:02.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Try?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.08,0:08:06.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I too have some of the organization's latest poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.44,0:08:13.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I make someone take it, we can\Nfind out if it really shrinks people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.96,0:08:16.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But who do we give it to?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.69,0:08:19.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The man we're dealing with tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.82,0:08:23.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as the deal is done,\Nwe're supposed to get rid of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.99,0:08:26.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the perfect{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ce to test the drug.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.43,0:08:31.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What if we do find out it shrinks people?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.15,0:08:35.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, we'll just kill the man\Nwe're dealing with, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.07,0:08:37.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...get rid of the kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:38.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.53,0:08:41.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Our orders are to take the kid back
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.72,0:08:45.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so the organization can investigate the drug's side-effects!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.24,0:08:47.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let people know the organization's secrets!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.87,0:08:48.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.67,0:08:50.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:54.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're doing things my way.\NDon't give me another corpse to carry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.96,0:08:56.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.92,0:09:01.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, did you tell the man\Nwhere tomorrow's deal is going down?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:03.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, using the usual method.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.53,0:09:07.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The deal is at 1:00 PM.\NGet sleep until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.11,0:09:17.61,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Alright. They're both fast asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.61,0:09:22.91,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Yikes! He's sleeping with the mask on!? Talk about creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.91,0:09:27.12,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Anyway, I need to get these\Nropes off and get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:29.33,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A wine bottle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.33,0:09:34.03,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Alright! Wrap it in this mat and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.03,0:09:38.74,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Crap! Did they hear that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:42.97,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Looks like I'm in the clear.\NOkay! Now to use a shard...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.72,0:09:48.77,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I somehow managed to get the rope off...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.77,0:09:52.06,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}...but how do I get\Nout of this first-floor room?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.06,0:09:56.15,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Even with the snow,\Nit'd be too dangerous to jump out...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.15,0:09:59.11,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Guess my only choice is\Nto hide in that fridge...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.28,0:10:04.07,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.07,0:10:08.37,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Oh! That wine must be\Ndripping somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.63,0:10:12.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.58,0:10:15.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What? The kid's gone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.08,0:10:18.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! He was gone when I got up!\NHe must've gone out the window!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.71,0:10:19.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.42,0:10:27.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He used the snow as a cushion to\Nget down! He's not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.89,0:10:31.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?!\NLet's go find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.85,0:10:35.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait. He's still here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.27,0:10:38.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.61,0:10:42.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He pretended to escape,\Nand is waiting for us to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.62,0:10:49.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.74,0:10:52.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,250)}Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.98,0:11:02.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my. Your hunch was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.12,0:11:05.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he has no place to go anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.02,0:11:08.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After today's deal is over,\Nwe'll find and eliminate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.27,0:11:17.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was sure I was done...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.60,0:11:22.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness I found this\Nstorage area beneath the mat then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.18,0:11:29.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Guess I'll look for that drug\Nwhile I have the{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ce!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.99,0:11:37.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, can't find it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.33,0:11:43.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Agasa said we could\Nfind a way to make me normal again
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.29,0:11:45.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,if we could figure out the drug's composition...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.59,0:11:49.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he took it all\Nfor today's deal...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.74,0:11:56.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this newspaper?\NIt has holes all over it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.21,0:12:00.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They must've cut out letters\Nto make a message
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.74,0:12:04.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,for the guy they're dealing with...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.06,0:12:09.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! They said they're\Ngoing to kill that guy! This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.69,0:12:14.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to find out where the deal is,\Nstop the murder, and get the drug!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.66,0:12:21.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Guessing the missing letters\Ngives me {\i1}i-te-ho-be-ru-ka{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.21,0:12:27.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rearranging them gives me "Beika Hotel..."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.00,0:12:28.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Beika Hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.97,0:12:34.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it doesn't specify where in the hotel.\NAre any other letters missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.85,0:12:42.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No luck, none have been cut out...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.12,0:12:44.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Cutter marks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.77,0:12:50.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! It was the August page\Nabove it that was cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,0:12:56.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means the August day\Nabove September 27th is... 30!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.08,0:13:01.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Beika Hotel 30!" That's where\Ntheir deal's taking place!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.74,0:13:03.70,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Beika Hotel
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.25,0:13:06.79,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But what does "Beika Hotel 30" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.81,0:13:11.48,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}This hotel only has 19 floors,\Nand there's no Room #30...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.48,0:13:14.26,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}#19? One moment, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.26,0:13:19.48,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That's it! It could be\Na baggage number! All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.48,0:13:20.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.59,0:13:21.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.46,0:13:26.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My daddy lost his number tag. It's #30...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.44,0:13:29.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,#30?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.02,0:13:33.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange.\NWe only have up to #26...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.99,0:13:35.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.86,0:13:38.49,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Damn! Where is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.49,0:13:42.87,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Crap! It's already past noon!\NAnd the deal is at 1:00!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.37,0:13:46.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! I forgot my wallet in the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.92,0:13:47.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.79,0:13:49.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did we park again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.34,0:13:51.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,#42. Here's the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.17,0:13:53.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I'll be right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.13,0:13:55.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,T-The parking lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.43,0:14:06.35,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}This is the car parked on #30...\NCould the deal be happening in here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.35,0:14:08.36,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But there's no one inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:10.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:12.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing to our car?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.53,0:14:15.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy! He must be a thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.57,0:14:19.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not like that! I just\Nthought it was a cool car!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.78,0:14:23.08,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}These people seem\Ncompletely unrelated...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.52,0:14:29.79,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Guess it's not here, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.79,0:14:32.30,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Whoa, a huge man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.17,0:14:37.72,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What's he looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.39,0:14:40.72,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The parking space number?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.02,0:14:47.89,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}There's a small "1" written\Nin chalk next to the "30"!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.89,0:14:51.98,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Ah! "301" must be\Na room number at this hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.98,0:14:56.25,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}And he's probably the guy\Nthey're dealing with!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.49,0:15:03.89,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The masked man!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.83,0:15:07.71,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}So this {\i1}is{\i0} where\Nthey're making the deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.38,0:15:13.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:16.05,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Oh, crap! I'm trapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.05,0:15:20.68,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That masked man will kill me\Nfor sure if he catches me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.68,0:15:24.77,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What do I do?! What do I do?!\NWhat do I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.85,0:15:30.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, Masao. The door locks by itself,\Nso you just need to close it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.35,0:15:32.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, be good while I'm gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.15,0:15:33.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Have fun, Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.65,0:15:35.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.49,0:15:40.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Burglar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.30,0:15:44.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh! I'm not a bad guy!\NI'm Space Detective Conan,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.58,0:15:48.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to catch evil aliens\Nfrom Planet Rampo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.41,0:15:51.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Liar! You're just a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.17,0:15:55.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm simply borrowing this\Nchild's form to deceive my foes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.42,0:15:57.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then show me your normal form!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.46,0:15:58.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.67,0:15:59.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}are{\i0} a burglar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.88,0:16:00.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.78,0:16:03.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just you wait! I'm gonna\Ncall the cops on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.12,0:16:05.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that, Masao! Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:08.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's my mommy's voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.48,0:16:12.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an alien from Planet Rampo!\NI can use any voice at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.36,0:16:16.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! That's awesome!\NYou really are a space detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.57,0:16:20.28,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Looks like I managed to fool him\Nwith this voice{\rHonorifics - Thoughts} chan{\r}ger...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.28,0:16:22.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Is there any way I can help?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.54,0:16:26.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There sure is! For now,\NI'd like to use your phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.21,0:16:28.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and do you have any chewing gum?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:32.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I do! But what for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.29,0:16:36.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.25,0:16:38.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've brought your food and wine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.88,0:16:41.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? We didn't order any.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.38,0:16:43.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? But we got a call earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.39,0:16:44.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:48.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. I {\i1}am{\i0} feeling hungry.\NHave it brought in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.68,0:16:49.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.89,0:16:52.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence! Bring it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.85,0:16:54.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Bring it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.86,0:16:56.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.91,0:17:00.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, pick up the pace!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:02.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.25,0:17:07.08,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Gum in the lock?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.58,0:17:16.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's start with a toast!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.04,0:17:20.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me first introduce\Nour other guest...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.01,0:17:24.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Other guest?! Don't tell me\Nthat kid's under here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.51,0:17:28.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What? He's not here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.31,0:17:33.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The cart's a decoy. He's really...\Ninside this closet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.84,0:17:36.18,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.18,0:17:37.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.25,0:17:39.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But when did he get in there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.11,0:17:43.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,While we were talking\Nwith the bellboy,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.19,0:17:47.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he put gum in the door to\Ndefeat the automatic lock.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.22,0:17:51.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He then snuck in while we\Nwere focused on the cart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.36,0:17:56.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think I'd fall\Nfor such a trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.54,0:18:00.46,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Damn! My only choice is\Nmy Anesthetic Watch Gun...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.47,0:18:02.01,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It won't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:07.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I had that interesting watch of yours\Ndisabled after we caught you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.21,0:18:08.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.35,0:18:12.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll regret the day\Nyou underestimated me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.39,0:18:15.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...high school detective Shin'ichi Kudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.86,0:18:22.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A toy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.36,0:18:29.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You still can't tell? It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.91,0:18:33.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The world-famous mystery writer,\NYusaku Kudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.90,0:18:38.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dad? Then don't\Ntell me that lady is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.54,0:18:41.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Shin{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.08,0:18:42.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.38,0:18:48.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But the fact you couldn't tell means\NI still have the skills as an actress!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.25,0:18:50.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means that big guy is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.55,0:18:51.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.68,0:18:53.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Agasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.19,0:18:58.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so mad!\NWe were worried too, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.80,0:19:03.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Shin{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}! We stopped\Nby the house and you were gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.23,0:19:07.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And then Dr. Agasa told you\Nabout how I shrank,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.94,0:19:10.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and then you cooked up this scheme?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.34,0:19:13.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I tested your detective skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.28,0:19:18.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And you successfully followed\Nall of our clues to make it this far!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.92,0:19:23.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything was just as I had calculated,\Nuntil you were shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.71,0:19:27.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So then you knew I was hiding\Nin that kitchen's storage area?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.39,0:19:31.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! Well, you just\Nbarely passed as a detective,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.90,0:19:35.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's your own fault for\Nnot realizing I was dressed as
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.90,0:19:38.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the Night Baron character\Nfrom my novels!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.48,0:19:42.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You jerk! That was no time for that!\NI thought I was about to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.87,0:19:48.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that so? Well, what do you say\Nwe leave this dangerous country
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.24,0:19:51.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and live together leisurely overseas?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.15,0:19:52.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.95,0:19:54.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Shin{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.45,0:19:59.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We did this so you would\Nrealize the situation you're in!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.12,0:20:04.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I helped out\Nwith their act, Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.59,0:20:11.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have friends in the Interpol.\NI'll have 'em look into this organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.34,0:20:15.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll get the drug at some point,\Nand you can be returned to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.81,0:20:20.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's put an end to this\Ndangerous detective game you're—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.28,0:20:21.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.69,0:20:25.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is {\i1}my{\i0} case! {\i1}I{\i0}'ll solve it!\NYou guys stay out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.62,0:20:27.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shin{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.15,0:20:31.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, I can't afford\Nto leave Japan yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.66,0:20:34.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.78,0:20:38.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.\NLet's humor him for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.13,0:20:39.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Honey...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.66,0:20:43.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But the instant things get dangerous,\Nwe're taking you overseas.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.40,0:20:47.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As it seems you have other reasons\Nfor not wanting to leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.91,0:20:52.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're leaving your son with us again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.38,0:20:56.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he insists on staying here...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.55,0:20:59.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.35,0:21:02.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here is his upbringing expense.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.96,0:21:05.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Use however much of it you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.92,0:21:09.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,10 million yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.09,0:21:12.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! I'd be delighted\Nto take care of your adorable
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.73,0:21:14.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and well-behaved son!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.98,0:21:17.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.77,0:21:18.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.44,0:21:23.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care of him for me.\NIt seems he likes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.30,0:21:25.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Really, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.84,0:21:26.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.52,0:21:28.77,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.95,0:23:07.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That sure was fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.62,0:23:11.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dropping my manuscripts and\Nescaping to Japan was worth it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.29,0:23:13.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But will Shin{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.91,0:23:17.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.\NHe'll admit defeat sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.13,0:23:20.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What do you say to a trip\Naround the world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.34,0:23:21.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that sounds great!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.42,0:23:22.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.80,0:23:28.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the foreign magazine editors!\NHow'd they find me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.26,0:23:30.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We got a call from your son!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.01,0:23:32.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now finish the last 308 pages!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.22,0:23:33.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw that! I'm first!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.52,0:23:35.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He stopped {\i1}our{\i0} presses!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.39,0:23:36.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He got us good.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.48,0:23:38.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, that little...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.14,0:23:49.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.44,0:23:57.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we can assume dynamite was planted in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.55,0:23:59.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,An act of tears?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.35,0:24:03.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This knife! Ryoji was behind this!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.22,0:24:08.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.57,0:24:14.53,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.53,0:24:19.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint: Fertilizer
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.96,0:24:21.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Next time, there's a surprising culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.33,0:24:24.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Hope to see you at our movie this year!
